# ── Project Kairos — environment template ──
# Every variable below is OPTIONAL. The static dashboard, REST API, and
# bundled analytics work off the committed SQLite database (`fund_data.db`)
# without any of these set. Configure the ones you need to take Kairos
# out of dry-run mode.

# ── Operational ──
# Persistent location for the SQLite store. Leave unset to use the bundled
# `fund_manager_tracker/fund_data.db`. On Vercel set to `/tmp/fund_data.db`
# if you want write access (note: ephemeral across cold starts).
# KAIROS_DB_PATH=

# ── LLM (Evidence Agent) ──
# Either provider unlocks LLM-driven evidence classification. The router
# tries Anthropic first, then NVIDIA, then falls back to a deterministic
# heuristic so the pipeline never blocks.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-...

# ── Evidence search ──
# Tavily powers the Monitor Agent's web search. Without it, Monitor Agent
# stays dormant and the UI surfaces this via /api/status.
# TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-...

# ── Email delivery (Alert Agent) ──
# Primary path: Resend HTTP API (https://resend.com) — serverless-friendly,
# no SMTP socket needed. Free tier sends from onboarding@resend.dev to your
# own verified address.
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
# RESEND_FROM_ADDRESS=Project Kairos <onboarding@resend.dev>
# KAIROS_ALERT_RECIPIENT=you@yourdomain.com

# ── Admin auth ──
# Shared secret gating privileged API actions (pipeline runs, outbound email).
# Without it those actions only work from localhost. Generate with:
#   python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(32))"
# KAIROS_ADMIN_TOKEN=
# CRON_SECRET=            # set in Vercel so cron invocations are authenticated

# Fallback path: classic SMTP. When neither Resend nor SMTP is configured,
# alert emails render to disk under `sent_emails/` instead of being sent.
# Perfect for demo runs.
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=alerts@yourdomain.com
# SMTP_PASSWORD=app-password
# SMTP_FROM_ADDRESS=alerts@yourdomain.com
# SMTP_STARTTLS=true

# ── WhatsApp delivery (Alert Agent) ──
# Optional. Without these the alert engine still ships email + on-screen.
# TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=AC...
# TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=...
# TWILIO_WHATSAPP_FROM=whatsapp:+14155238886
